title: Webinar: Dev Superpowers - AngularJS
eventShortDescription: ​AngularJS is a client-side javascript framework that enables the creation of impressively dynamic user interfaces. It strives to remove the tedium of manipulating DOM elements by abstracting many common functions such as showing/hiding, updating content and injecting/removing elements. Join Ben as he transforms a rigid MVC web application into a dynamic pleasure using AngularJS.
